  (text "Input protection capture notes:\n- ADR-0018 selects LM74930-Q1 hard cutoff and permits load disconnection during load dump\n- Q2 IAUTN15S6N025ATMA1 150 V is the raw-side HGATE cutoff FET\n- Q1 IAUT300N08S5N012ATMA2 80 V is the protected DGATE reverse FET\n- R3/R4/R5 42.2k+42.2k/1.00k 1% set a generated 48.99-54.89 V cutoff\n- D1 SM8S33AHM3/I is DNP legacy footprint only and is not an approved energy sink\n- Q1 cooling is passive PCB copper plus thermal pad to the metal enclosure\n- Tj target is <=150 C and the full 125 C ambient thermal path is <=6.20 K/W\n- RSH1/U2 retain total input current monitoring\n\nNo PCB layout or manufacturing output is authorized by this capture."
    (at 20 20 0)
    (effects (font (size 2.0 2.0)) (justify left top))
